  "detailed_description": "X-Force Under Attack brings back all the charm of shmup games from the 80's/90's. It's a frenetic and chaotic space shooter with insane battles against extremely difficult bosses. Embark on epic battles and stop enemies from establishing a military base orbiting the planet Genesis<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bullet Hell</h2><br>Defeat several enemies and hundreds of projectiles, coming from all sides at the same time.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446740/extras/9d3cfd17487cf039708c3ee9c9510d78.poster.avif?t=1751467648\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446740/extras/9d3cfd17487cf039708c3ee9c9510d78.webm?t=1751467648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446740/extras/9d3cfd17487cf039708c3ee9c9510d78.mp4?t=1751467648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ships</h2><br>Select the ship that best suits you. Each ship has unique attributes that make it best for a specific player type and stage, so choose wisely.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446740/extras/5fb1b2c3b819544dea8d132918cd77fe.poster.avif?t=1751467648\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446740/extras/5fb1b2c3b819544dea8d132918cd77fe.webm?t=1751467648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446740/extras/5fb1b2c3b819544dea8d132918cd77fe.mp4?t=1751467648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bosses</h2><br>Fight gigantic, intimidating bosses, each one more difficult than the last, and defeat them to end an era of tyranny.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446740/extras/12a58fb5068697a9e0297c1948754150.poster.avif?t=1751467648\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446740/extras/12a58fb5068697a9e0297c1948754150.webm?t=1751467648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446740/extras/12a58fb5068697a9e0297c1948754150.mp4?t=1751467648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Adventure through 10 beautiful and unique levels.<br></li><li>Defeat the gigantic bosses spread throughout space.<br></li><li>Make upgrades to your ship to be able to fight and defeat enemies.<br></li><li>Use Power-ups to annihilate various shots and enemies on the screen.<br></li><li>Dodge comets lost in space<br></li><li>And much more.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "X-Force Under Attack brings back all the charm of shmup games from the 80's/90's. It's a frenetic and chaotic space shooter with insane battles against extremely difficult bosses. Embark on epic battles and stop enemies from establishing a military base orbiting the planet Genesis<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bullet Hell</h2><br>Defeat several enemies and hundreds of projectiles, coming from all sides at the same time.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446740/extras/9d3cfd17487cf039708c3ee9c9510d78.poster.avif?t=1751467648\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446740/extras/9d3cfd17487cf039708c3ee9c9510d78.webm?t=1751467648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446740/extras/9d3cfd17487cf039708c3ee9c9510d78.mp4?t=1751467648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ships</h2><br>Select the ship that best suits you. Each ship has unique attributes that make it best for a specific player type and stage, so choose wisely.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446740/extras/5fb1b2c3b819544dea8d132918cd77fe.poster.avif?t=1751467648\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446740/extras/5fb1b2c3b819544dea8d132918cd77fe.webm?t=1751467648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446740/extras/5fb1b2c3b819544dea8d132918cd77fe.mp4?t=1751467648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bosses</h2><br>Fight gigantic, intimidating bosses, each one more difficult than the last, and defeat them to end an era of tyranny.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446740/extras/12a58fb5068697a9e0297c1948754150.poster.avif?t=1751467648\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446740/extras/12a58fb5068697a9e0297c1948754150.webm?t=1751467648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446740/extras/12a58fb5068697a9e0297c1948754150.mp4?t=1751467648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Adventure through 10 beautiful and unique levels.<br></li><li>Defeat the gigantic bosses spread throughout space.<br></li><li>Make upgrades to your ship to be able to fight and defeat enemies.<br></li><li>Use Power-ups to annihilate various shots and enemies on the screen.<br></li><li>Dodge comets lost in space<br></li><li>And much more.</li></ul>",
